"the retry limit. Re-authorise it on the ESI scopes page (/auth/scopes/) to "
"resume ingestion; corp {scopes} pages will show stale data until then."
msgstr ""
"コーポデータの取り込み（{scopes}）を認可している {character_name} の ESI "
