"FORCA integration health has degraded:\n"
"\n"
"{details}\n"
"\n"
"Open the Admin Console → Health page for the full picture. This alert fires "
"once per distinct problem set and resets automatically once healthy."
msgstr ""
"FORCA の連携の健全性が低下しました:\n"
"\n"
"{details}\n"
"\n"
