#: apps/planetary/services.py
msgid "No live colony of this type imported yet."
msgstr "このタイプの実コロニーはまだインポートされていません。"

#: apps/planetary/services.py
msgid "Your live colony is pulling a different product than the plan expects."
msgstr "実コロニーが採取している産出物がプランの想定と異なります。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "The all-rounder. Great first planet."
msgstr "オールラウンダー。最初の惑星に最適です。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Balanced and forgiving — food, industrial and electronics feedstock. If "
"you're new, start here."
msgstr ""
"バランスが良く扱いやすい — 食料、産業用、電子部品の原料が採れます。初心者はこ"
"こから始めましょう。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Robotics & electronics feedstock."
msgstr "ロボティクスと電子部品の原料。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Reliable all-rounder rich in metals and organics. Backbone of most "
"electronics and robotics chains."
msgstr ""
"金属と有機物が豊富な、信頼できるオールラウンダー。ほとんどの電子部品・ロボ"
"ティクス系チェーンの基盤です。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Construction metals & heavy industry."
msgstr "建設用金属と重工業。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Metals and magma — the source of construction materials and many high-end "
"refined commodities."
msgstr "金属とマグマ — 建設資材や多くの高級精製品の供給源です。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "High-end electronics & metals."
msgstr "高級電子部品と金属。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Harsh but valuable: heavy metals and non-CS crystals that feed advanced "
"electronics and superconductors."
msgstr ""
"過酷だが価値が高い。先端電子部品や超伝導体の原料となる重金属や非CSクリスタル"
"が採れます。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Coolant, life-support & fuels."
msgstr "冷却材、生命維持、燃料。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Cold storage of gases, water and microorganisms — coolant, oxygen and "
"biotech chains start here."
msgstr ""
"ガス、水、微生物の低温貯蔵庫 — 冷却材、酸素、バイオテック系チェーンの起点で"
"す。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Fuels, oxidisers & industrials."
msgstr "燃料、酸化剤 & 工業品。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"The only source of Reactive Gas. Gas planets drive oxidising compounds, "
"oxygen and fuel chains."
msgstr ""
"Reactive Gas の唯一の供給源。ガス惑星は酸化化合物、酸素、燃料チェーンを支えま"
"す。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Biotech & strong food chains."
msgstr "バイオテック & 強力な食物チェーン。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Water-rich and organic — the best planet for biomass, proteins and the "
"biotech P3/P4 lines."
msgstr ""
"水と有機物が豊富 — バイオマス、タンパク質、バイオテック P3/P4 ラインに最適な"
"惑星。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Electronics feedstock (plasmoids)."
msgstr "電子機器の原料(plasmoids)。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Electrically charged: plasmoids, ionic solutions and noble gas for the "
"electronics and superconductor chains."
msgstr ""
"帯電:電子機器・超伝導チェーン向けの plasmoids、ionic solutions、noble gas。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Extraction planet"
msgstr "採取惑星"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Pull one or two raw P0 resources and refine them on-site into P1 (or "
"straight P2 if you have the feedstock)."
msgstr ""
"1〜2 種類の P0 を採取し、その場で精製して P1 にします（材料が揃うなら直接 P2 "
"まで）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (sets your power/CPU budget — upgrade it fully)."
msgstr ""
"コマンドセンター ×1（電力／CPU の上限を決めます — 必ず最大までアップグレー"
"ド）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"1× Extractor Control Unit per resource, with as many extractor heads as CPU/"
"PG allows (more heads = more yield, but shorter reach)."
msgstr ""
"リソース 1 種につきエクストラクターコントロールユニット ×1。CPU／PG が許す限"
"りエクストラクターヘッドを増やします（ヘッドが多いほど産出量は増えますが射程"
"は短くなります）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Basic Industry Facilities to convert P0 → P1 (each does 3,000 P0 → 20 P1 "
"every 30 min)."
msgstr ""
"P0 → P1 を変換するベーシックインダストリーファシリティ（1 基あたり 30 分ごと"
"に P0 3,000 → P1 20）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad as the export point and buffer storage."
msgstr "ローンチパッド ×1。輸出ポイント兼バッファ用ストレージとして使います。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Route extractor output → storage/launchpad → factories → launchpad. Keep the "
"extracted P0 flowing into the BIFs and the finished P1 to the launchpad for "
"export."
msgstr ""
"ルートは エクストラクター産出 → ストレージ／ローンチパッド → ファクトリー → "
"ローンチパッド。採取した P0 を BIF に流し続け、完成した P1 は輸出用にローンチ"
"パッドへ送ります。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export P1 (or P2) via the customs office. Import nothing."
msgstr "カスタムオフィス経由で P1（または P2）を輸出します。輸入は不要です。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import cheaper lower-tier materials and refine them up a tier. No extraction "
"— pure manufacturing throughput."
msgstr ""
"安い下位ティアの材料を輸入し、1 ティア上に精製します。採取はなし — 純粋な製造"
"スループット勝負です。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center (upgrade fully for CPU/PG)."
msgstr "コマンドセンター ×1（CPU／PG のために最大までアップグレード）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad to receive imports and hold exports."
msgstr "ローンチパッド ×1。輸入品の受け取りと輸出品の保管に使います。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"As many Advanced Industry Facilities as your power/CPU allows (each does "
"40+40 input → 5 output every hour for P2)."
msgstr ""
"電力／CPU が許す限りアドバンストインダストリーファシリティを設置します（P2 の"
"場合、1 基あたり 1 時間ごとに材料 40+40 → 産出 5）。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities to buffer inputs between imports."
msgstr "輸入と輸入の間に材料をためておくストレージファシリティ。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Import inputs to the launchpad → route to each factory → route finished "
"goods back to the launchpad."
msgstr ""
"材料をローンチパッドに輸入 → 各ファクトリーへルート → 完成品をローンチパッド"
"へ戻すルート。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Import the P1/P2 inputs; export the higher-tier product."
msgstr "P1／P2 の材料を輸入し、上位ティアの製品を輸出します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage / staging planet"
msgstr "保管 / ステージング惑星"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A buffer or consolidation point. Rare for most pilots — usually a launchpad "
"on another planet does the job."
msgstr ""
"バッファまたは集約用の拠点。多くのパイロットには不要です — 通常は他の惑星の"
"ローンチパッドで事足ります。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Command Center"
msgstr "コマンドセンター ×1"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "1× Launchpad"
msgstr "ローンチパッド ×1"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Storage facilities as needed."
msgstr "必要に応じてストレージファシリティを設置。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Consolidate goods here before a single haul out."
msgstr "一度に運び出す前に、ここで物資を集約します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Export in bulk on your haul day."
msgstr "運搬日にまとめて輸出します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Not upgrading the Command Center"
msgstr "コマンドセンターをアップグレードしない"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Your Command Center level sets your entire CPU/PG budget. Upgrade it to "
"level 5 before you place facilities, or you'll run out of power halfway "
"through."
msgstr ""
"コマンドセンターのレベルが CPU/PG の総枠を決めます。施設を配置する前にレベル "
"5 までアップグレードしないと、途中で電力が尽きます。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Routing errors"
msgstr "ルーティングのミス"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"A facility with no inbound route sits idle; a route to the wrong storage "
"stalls the chain. Follow every product from extractor → factory → launchpad."
msgstr ""
"入力ルートのない施設は停止したままになり、誤ったストレージへのルートはチェー"
"ン全体を止めます。すべての製品をエクストラクター → ファクトリー → ローンチ"
"パッドまで追跡してください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Too many extractor heads"
msgstr "エクストラクターヘッドの付けすぎ"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"More heads raise yield but shorten the extraction radius and cost CPU/PG. "
"Balance heads against the program length you actually want to run."
msgstr ""
"ヘッドを増やすと産出は上がりますが、採取半径が短くなり CPU/PG を消費します。"
"実際に回したいプログラム長とのバランスを取ってください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Insufficient storage"
msgstr "ストレージ不足"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"If a launchpad or storage fills up, upstream facilities stop. Size storage "
"for the time between your resets."
msgstr ""
"ローンチパッドやストレージが満杯になると、上流の施設が停止します。リセット間"
"隔に見合う容量を確保してください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wrong schematic"
msgstr "スキーマティックの誤り"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Setting a factory to the wrong schematic wastes materials. Double-check "
"inputs match what you're actually routing in."
msgstr ""
"ファクトリーに誤ったスキーマティックを設定すると素材を無駄にします。入力素材"
"が実際にルーティングしているものと一致しているか再確認してください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Overbuilding factories"
msgstr "ファクトリーの作りすぎ"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Ten factories starved of feedstock earn less than three that run "
"continuously. Match factory count to your extraction rate."
msgstr ""
"素材が足りない 10 基のファクトリーより、途切れずに稼働する 3 基のほうが稼げま"
"す。ファクトリー数は採取レートに合わせてください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Ignoring customs (POCO) tax"
msgstr "カスタムオフィス（POCO）税の無視"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid ""
"Export/import tax at the customs office is charged on every launch. In "
"hostile space it can dwarf your margin — factor it in before you commit."
msgstr ""
"カスタムオフィスの輸出入税は打ち上げのたびに課されます。敵対空域では利益を軽"
"く食い潰すこともあります — 動く前に計算に入れてください。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Train Command Center Upgrades to unlock the planet tiers you need."
msgstr ""
"必要な惑星ティアを解放するために Command Center Upgrades をトレーニングしま"
"す。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Buy and deploy a Command Center on each planet, then upgrade it fully."
msgstr "各惑星にコマンドセンターを購入・展開し、最大までアップグレードします。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "On extraction planets: place the ECU, add heads, and start a program."
msgstr "採取惑星では、ECU を設置してヘッドを追加し、プログラムを開始します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Place your factories and set the correct schematic on each."
msgstr "ファクトリーを配置し、それぞれに正しいスキーマティックを設定します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Wire the routes: extractor → storage → factory → launchpad."
msgstr ""
"ルートを繋ぎます: エクストラクター → ストレージ → ファクトリー → ローンチパッ"
"ド。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Confirm the customs office tax for your space and your standings."
msgstr "自分の空域とスタンディングに応じたカスタムオフィス税を確認します。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Set a reset cadence that matches your extractor program length."
msgstr "エクストラクターのプログラム長に合わせたリセット間隔を決めます。"

#: apps/planetary/static_data.py
msgid "Haul exports to your chosen market hub (or hand to corp buyback)."
msgstr ""
"輸出品を選んだマーケットハブまで運搬します（またはコーポの buyback に出しま"
"す）。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing planets"
msgstr "プラネット未設定"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Not costed"
msgstr "コスト未計算"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Missing prices"
msgstr "価格未設定"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Unprofitable"
msgstr "赤字"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Profitable"
msgstr "黒字"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "The Planetary Industry planner is currently disabled by leadership."
msgstr ""
"Planetary Industry プランナーは現在リーダーシップによって無効化されています。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Add at least one planet — that's what the plan is built around."
msgstr ""
"少なくとも1つプラネットを追加してください — プランはそれを中心に組み立てられ"
"ます。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Each factory planet needs a product to build — pick one."
msgstr ""
"各ファクトリープラネットには生産する製品が必要です — 1つ選んでください。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Plan “%(name)s” created — here's your setup and profit estimate."
msgstr "プラン “%(name)s” を作成しました — こちらが構成と利益の見積もりです。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Plan updated and re-costed."
msgstr "プランを更新し、再計算しました。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Keep at least one planet on the plan."
msgstr "プランには少なくとも1つプラネットを残してください。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Re-costed with the latest market prices."
msgstr "最新のマーケット価格で再計算しました。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Duplicated as “%(name)s”."
msgstr "“%(name)s” として複製しました。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Status set to %(status)s."
msgstr "ステータスを %(status)s に設定しました。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” archived. Delete again to remove it permanently."
msgstr ""
"“%(name)s” をアーカイブしました。もう一度削除すると完全に削除されます。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "“%(name)s” permanently deleted."
msgstr "“%(name)s” を完全に削除しました。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "A colony sync is already running — give it a minute before retrying."
msgstr "コロニー同期はすでに実行中です — 1分ほど待ってから再試行してください。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
#, python-format
msgid "Colony sync queued for %(count)s pilot(s) — refresh in a minute."
msgstr ""
"%(count)s 人のパイロットのコロニー同期をキューに追加しました — 1分後に更新し"
"てください。"

#: apps/planetary/views.py
msgid "Grant the Planetary Industry scope first, then sync your colonies."
msgstr ""
"まず Planetary Industry スコープを許可してから、コロニーを同期してください。"

#: apps/procurement/contracts.py
msgid "That contract is no longer in the snapshot."
msgstr "そのコントラクトはスナップショットに存在しません。"

#: apps/procurement/contracts.py
msgid "That contract is not a valid match for this order."
msgstr "そのコントラクトはこの発注書と一致しません。"

#: apps/procurement/forms.py
msgid "The per-cycle quantity must be at least 1."
msgstr "サイクルあたりの数量は1以上である必要があります。"

#: apps/procurement/forms.py
msgid "Order at least one unit."
msgstr "1ユニット以上を発注してください。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Estimated cycle value at or above which a supply agreement needs a second "
"Director's approval."
msgstr ""
"この推定サイクル金額以上の供給契約には、2人目の Director の承認が必要になりま"
"す。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Total value at or above which a standalone purchase order (one not covered "
"by an active agreement) needs Director approval."
msgstr ""
"この合計金額以上の単独発注書（有効な契約の対象外のもの）には、 Director の承"
"認が必要になります。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Days past the promised date before a purchase order is flagged overdue."
msgstr "発注書が期限超過としてフラグされるまでの、納期からの経過日数。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Complete weeks of closed purchase orders the reliability rollup looks back "
"over."
msgstr "信頼性の集計が遡って参照する、クローズ済み発注書の完全な週数。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Arm the contract matcher (runs after the corp-contracts sync). Off: officers "
"confirm contract matches by hand."
msgstr ""
"コントラクトマッチャーを有効化します（ corp のコントラクト同期の後に実行）。"
"オフの場合: オフィサーが手動でコントラクトの一致を確認します。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Arm the wallet-journal payment reconcile. Off: officers confirm payments by "
"hand."
msgstr ""
"ウォレットジャーナルの支払照合を有効化します。オフの場合: オフィサーが手動で"
"支払を確認します。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Arm the daily overdue sweep (also expires lapsed agreements)."
msgstr ""
"日次の期限超過スイープを有効化します（失効した契約の期限切れ処理も行いま"
"す）。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Let a finished matched contract post its landed quantities as receipts "
"automatically. Off: officers post receipts by hand."
msgstr ""
"一致した完了コントラクトが、着荷数量を入荷として自動計上できるようにします。"
"オフの場合: オフィサーが手動で入荷を計上します。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Arm the nightly supplier-reliability rollup."
msgstr "夜間のサプライヤー信頼性ロールアップを有効化します。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid ""
"Wallet-journal ref_types the payment reconcile treats as supplier payments. "
"Enumerate from the real corp journal before arming."
msgstr ""
"支払照合がサプライヤー支払として扱うウォレットジャーナルの ref_types 。有効化"
"する前に、実際の corp ジャーナルから列挙してください。"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "procurement config"
msgstr "調達設定"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "procurement configs"
msgstr "調達設定"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Market hub"
msgstr "マーケット hub"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Probation"
msgstr "試用期間"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Suspended"
msgstr "停止中"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Fixed price"
msgstr "固定価格"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Jita-indexed + premium"
msgstr "Jita 相場連動 + プレミアム"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "One-off"
msgstr "単発"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Monthly"
msgstr "月次"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Prepaid"
msgstr "前払い"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "On delivery"
msgstr "納品時払い"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Net 7 days"
msgstr "支払期日7日"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Net 30 days"
msgstr "支払期日30日"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Contract expected"
msgstr "コントラクト待ち"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Contract available"
msgstr "コントラクト利用可能"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Partially delivered"
msgstr "一部納品"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Reconciled"
msgstr "照合済み"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Disputed"
msgstr "係争中"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Supplier delivers"
msgstr "サプライヤーが納品"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Hub pickup (corp hauls)"
msgstr "hub 引き取り（ corp が輸送）"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Auto (contract landed)"
msgstr "自動（コントラクト着荷）"

#: apps/procurement/models.py
msgid "Manual (officer attested)"
msgstr "手動（オフィサー確認）"

#: apps/procurement/payments.py
msgid "That wallet entry no longer exists."
msgstr "そのウォレット記録は存在しません。"

#: apps/procurement/payments.py
msgid "That payment is already matched to another order."
msgstr "その支払はすでに別の発注書に紐付けられています。"

#: apps/procurement/payments.py
msgid "This order is already settled."
msgstr "この発注書はすでに決済済みです。"

#: apps/procurement/receipts.py
msgid "This purchase order is not ready to receive deliveries."
msgstr "この発注書は入荷を受け付ける状態ではありません。"

#: apps/procurement/receipts.py
msgid "This line is already fully received."
msgstr "この明細はすでに全量入荷済みです。"

#: apps/procurement/receipts.py
msgid "Receipt quantity must be positive."
msgstr "入荷数量は正の値である必要があります。"

#: apps/procurement/receipts.py
msgid "Only a hub-pickup purchase order needs a corp haul."
msgstr "corp 輸送が必要なのは hub 引き取りの発注書のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/receipts.py
msgid "This purchase order is not ready to be hauled yet."
msgstr "この発注書はまだ輸送できる状態ではありません。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only a draft agreement can be submitted."
msgstr "提出できるのはドラフト状態の契約のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "An approval request for this agreement is already open."
msgstr "この契約の承認リクエストはすでに発行されています。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "This approval is no longer pending."
msgstr "この承認はすでに保留状態ではありません。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "You can't approve your own agreement — another Director must."
msgstr ""
"自分の契約を承認することはできません — 別の Director が行う必要があります。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
#, python-format
msgid "Agreement %(outcome)s."
msgstr "契約を %(outcome)s しました。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only a draft purchase order can be submitted."
msgstr "提出できるのはドラフト状態の発注書のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "A purchase order needs at least one line."
msgstr "発注書には少なくとも1件の明細が必要です。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "The supplier does not sell every item on this order."
msgstr ""
"このサプライヤーは、この発注書のすべての品目を取り扱っているわけではありませ"
"ん。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only a submitted purchase order can be approved."
msgstr "承認できるのは提出済みの発注書のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "You can't approve your own purchase order — another officer must."
msgstr ""
"自分の発注書を承認することはできません — 別のオフィサーが行う必要があります。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid ""
"A standalone purchase order at or above the Director threshold needs "
"Director approval."
msgstr "Director しきい値以上の単独発注書には、 Director の承認が必要です。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only an approved purchase order can be marked contract-expected."
msgstr "コントラクト待ちにできるのは承認済みの発注書のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "This purchase order is already closed."
msgstr "この発注書はすでにクローズされています。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only a Director can cancel a purchase order this far along."
msgstr "この段階まで進んだ発注書をキャンセルできるのは Director のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "A dispute needs a reason."
msgstr "係争には理由が必要です。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "Only an in-flight purchase order can be disputed."
msgstr "係争にできるのは進行中の発注書のみです。"

#: apps/procurement/services.py
msgid "This purchase order is not under dispute."
msgstr "この発注書は係争中ではありません。"

