"Every leadership control in one place — roles, doctrines, readiness, "
"rewards, services, structures, alerts and intelligence — with a full audit "
"trail and no database to touch."
msgstr ""
"リーダーシップに必要な操作をすべて一か所に。ロール、doctrine、即応性、報酬、"
