msgstr "新規パイロットには \"Snuggly\" の代わりに \"Learning\" を表示"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/combat_settings.html
msgid "Activity floor (kills + losses)"
msgstr "アクティビティ下限（キル + ロス）"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/combat_settings.html
msgid "Below this total, the danger label is softened."
msgstr "この合計を下回ると、危険度ラベルが緩和されます。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/combat_settings.html
msgid "Save newbro settings"
msgstr "newbro 設定を保存"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/hub.html
msgid "Auto-AAR"
msgstr "Auto-AAR"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Auto-AAR on notable battles"
msgstr "注目の戦闘での Auto-AAR"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"When a fight crosses a threshold below, FORCA queues a <a "
"href=\"%(battles_url)s\" class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">battle AAR</a> "
"automatically — no officer has to remember. Ships <strong class=\"text-"
"ink\">off</strong>; one AAR per battle, capped per run, and it rides the LLM "
"rate caps. A threshold of 0 disables that trigger."
msgstr ""
"戦闘が以下のしきい値を超えると、FORCA が自動的に <a href=\"%(battles_url)s\" "
"class=\"text-cyan hover:underline\">battle AAR</a> をキューに入れます — オ"
"フィサーが覚えておく必要はありません。出荷時は <strong class=\"text-"
"ink\">off</strong> です。1 戦闘につき AAR は 1 件、実行ごとに上限があり、LLM "
"のレート上限に従います。しきい値を 0 にするとそのトリガーは無効になります。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Auto-AAR enabled"
msgstr "Auto-AAR 有効"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "— arm the scan (kill switch)"
msgstr "— スキャンをアーム (キルスイッチ)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Notability thresholds"
msgstr "注目度のしきい値"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Min ISK swing"
msgstr "最小 ISK 収支差"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Absolute ISK destroyed − lost. 0 = off."
msgstr "破壊 ISK − 損失 ISK の絶対値。0 = オフ。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Min our losses"
msgstr "自軍ロスの最小件数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Min logi lost"
msgstr "logi ロスの最小件数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Min off-doctrine losses"
msgstr "doctrine 外ロスの最小件数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Scan limits"
msgstr "スキャンの上限"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Lookback (hours)"
msgstr "遡及期間 (時間)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Max AARs per run"
msgstr "1 回の実行あたりの最大 AAR 数"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Caps LLM spend on a busy night."
msgstr "忙しい夜の LLM 消費に上限を設けます。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/auto_aar.html
msgid "Save auto-AAR settings"
msgstr "auto-AAR 設定を保存"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/command_intel/autonomous.html
msgid "Command Intelligence · Autonomous proposals"
msgstr "コマンドインテリジェンス · 自律提案"

