msgstr "アンバー"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/dimensions.html
#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/kpis.html
#: templates/corporation/standings.html
msgid "Red"
msgstr "レッド"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/dimensions.html
msgid "Restores every dimension's weight and bands to the shipped defaults."
msgstr "すべての領域の重みと帯を出荷時のデフォルトに戻します。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid "Readiness · Doctrine classification"
msgstr "即応性 · Doctrine 分類"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid ""
"Mark which doctrines are <span class=\"text-ink\">primary</span>, <span "
"class=\"text-ink\">mandatory</span> or <span class=\"text-ink\">alliance</"
"span>, set a retirement date, and a minimum pilot count. A <span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">mandatory</span> doctrine that's under-crewed raises a "
"high-severity finding; a doctrine past its <span class=\"text-"
"cyan\">retirement date</span> raises a replace-it finding. Leaving a "
"doctrine unclassified has no effect on the index."
msgstr ""
"どの doctrine が <span class=\"text-ink\">primary</span>、<span class=\"text-"
"ink\">必須</span>、<span class=\"text-ink\">アライアンス</span> かを指定し、"
"終了日と最小パイロット数を設定します。<span class=\"text-cyan\">必須</span> "
"の doctrine の人員が不足している場合は深刻度「高」の検出結果が発生し、<span "
"class=\"text-cyan\">終了日</span> を過ぎた doctrine は置き換えを促す検出結果"
"が発生します。doctrine を未分類のままにしても指数には影響しません。"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid "Primary"
msgstr "Primary"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
msgid "Retires"
msgstr "終了日"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/doctrines.html
