#: templates/admin_audit/console/retention_settings.html
msgid ""
"How long each class of data is kept before the nightly\n"
"    housekeeping job prunes it, and what happens to a member's data when "
"they leave. These drive the\n"
"    daily retention task."
msgstr ""
"各種データが毎晩のハウスキーピングジョブで削除されるまでの保持期間と、メン"
