#: templates/planetary/_onboarding.html
msgid ""
"You deploy colonies on planets. <span class=\"text-ink\">Extractor</span> "
"planets pull\n"
"    raw resources and refine them; <span class=\"text-ink\">factory</span> "
"planets combine\n"
"    materials into higher-value goods. Reset the extractors on your own "
"schedule, haul the\n"
"    output to market, and it earns while you're doing other things. Taxes, "
"hauling and\n"
"    market prices decide whether it's worth it — this planner does that "
"maths for you."
msgstr ""
"惑星に colony を配備します。<span class=\"text-ink\">Extractor</span> 惑星は"
"原材料を採取して精製し、<span class=\"text-ink\">factory</span> 惑星は素材を"
"組み合わせてより価値の高い製品にします。extractor は自分のスケジュールでリ"
"セットし、産出物を市場まで haul すれば、他のことをしている間に稼いでくれま"
"す。税金、輸送、市場価格が採算を左右します — このプランナーがその計算を代わり"
"に行います。"

